claim.claim-text:
1. A transceiver module for a fiber optic communications system comprising: 
a housing; 
a connector for connecting with the housing; 
an optical sub assembly (OSA) installed within the connector for receiving or emitting optical signals; 
a printed circuit board (PCB) installed within the housing for processing photoelectric signals; and 
a clipping device disposed within the housing for fixing the optical sub assembly so that the optical sub assembly is electrically connected with the printed circuit board.
